If you want to use a base map that isn’t available from Mapbox, you may want to take a look at the ggmap package which has a few more options. You can also make a custom basemaps using the Mapbox studio.↩︎
I ordered these photos by longitude so, in Baltimore, the numbers appear on the map in order from left to right. If I sorted in descending order by latitude instead, the numbers would have appeared on the map from top to bottom.↩︎
